## What Each Type Gives You in RAG

| Content Type | What Gets Embedded | What Gets Returned to LLM |
|---|---|---|
| `text` | Raw text | Raw text |
| `table` | Short summary + headers | Full markdown table |
| `image` | Caption / alt text | Image path/base64 for UI |

